Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.23,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(545,617)}{\fad(300,300)}第 8 话  『超麻烦呢』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这个二年级的有什么事么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙不是被人讨厌的山田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没事找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把后面的大家伙交出来 那边的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶 你要找诺亚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是山田前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找诺亚什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你装傻也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年级引起骚乱的那些事我全都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真困扰啊 为什么诺亚会被怀疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是那三人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚可是有阻止他们的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是他们没有听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙 打算装傻到最后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就用强的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说回来啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得年下的女人怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实诺亚啊 喜欢年长的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…也不是年下的人就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说前辈喜欢上诺亚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶？这女人搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说…对我有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泷川 那话就和我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}复制这家伙的能力 反过来抓住她的弱点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什么啊 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说我只不过调戏一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟然还当真了 真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果是你被她戏耍了 然后滚回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是个不好对付的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是去劝说被泷上操纵的三人比较有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次一定要亲到她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这算什么啊 缠着别人接吻真是太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别再出现在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 怎么能那么简单就放弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 泷川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要不要加入到我的伙伴中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还在期待什么有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也让我参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈？你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你想靠这么说来接近诺亚也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说你太烦人了 还很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 但是我可是全部都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括你使用魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟我们是超常现象研究部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是对那些事情非常了解哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是不让我加入的话 损失的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌啦 那你就早说啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道前辈你知道其他魔女的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 真的知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就如你所愿让你入伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为交换 告诉我其他魔女的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么…有什么不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我成为伙伴这件事就当我没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看那个样子是全灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 足球部的涉谷说是因为个人的理由而拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说和泷川只是很好的朋友罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深泽也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是泷川诺亚用魔女的力量封住了他们的口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那边怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}复仇成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没 以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是很让人恶心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总而言之今天就解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 我有一件想让你们三个人去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 在我刚说出魔女的事情的时候 那家伙的脸就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说那家伙的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们俩 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点去活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是谁做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笔记的上卷不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吧 到底是谁干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是这样做真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些都是为了你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不用做到退学的地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说到底我们真的能成为魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山崎你在隐藏什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我那女人的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}否则 我就不管这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就全告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年级c组的泷川诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消除这所学校里其他的魔女们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女 消除？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田同学你知道学校里魔女会被继承的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且你应该也注意到另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女的能力是具有烦恼或纠纷的人得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是这么个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泷川诺亚先用看见过去的能力掌握学生的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他们惹出麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后企图让烦恼缠身的他们成为下一届魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并且继承能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她手里有笔记的上下卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此一来 接下来终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 收拾干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别吓我们啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一个目标就是我们魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个女人这次打算把学校的魔女都消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么消除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是字面的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如退学之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家不要小丽退学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个混蛋眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么一开始不告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说你知道的也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为这个学校的学生会长的话就得这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅小丽和小田切同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有大冢同学和猿岛同学也可能会被盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超研部的活动是不是先停一停比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 被泷川找到只不过是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此不如主动出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能让大家置身于危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没问题哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为山田同学也和我们一样危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且不知道为什么我心里很激动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不了 没必要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 互换成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点把她带出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就和你说的一样呢 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放弃吧 问题儿童们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们真是活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到山田和白石已经互换了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是发生和白石同学互换的事件的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就得考虑下退学的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是我们道高一丈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话 已经只能对泷川言听计从了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚是我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你们所谓的朋友要你们破坏活动室 袭击白石的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是泷川同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来口风很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不怎愿意 只有拿她们当人质来说服泷川了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我有一个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找诺亚有什么事吗 各位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 已经暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这叫什么好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你们互换之后的演技太差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不想被你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 正如你所看到的 泷川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们已经被囚禁在超研部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快停止让魔女退学的计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得我会照做吗 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是交换条件的话 倒是可以答应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把笔记的上卷还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把那三个人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是诺亚重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交换条件 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么我把下卷也给你们 这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 你的目的是笔记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要把笔记交给你们不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说过了 停止让魔女退学的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的要求 只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因为不能答应这个所以才提出交换条件的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说实话好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 这样啊 那么谈判破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就这么回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差一点就可以拿回笔记了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因为山田无聊的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那里无聊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们之前的目的不就是阻止她的计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为这三个人一定是被泷川操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然不惜交出笔记来交换他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 干脆用魅惑的能力来拉拢他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有这个不要 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你们不收手的话 我们也没有其他办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会放弃魔女的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深泽 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要让我们回去 我们一定会说服泷川同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不想让她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们真的觉得这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比一起个人 还是四个人一起更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样 我就没什么好说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是告白的话 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 你以为是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我觉得不太可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会是想说用魔女的力量来统治学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个嘛…和你说的差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好遗憾 差一点点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是这样的话 你还真是有够无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此居然甘愿被人讨厌 来引发那样的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算没有魔女的力量 他们也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得他们三人真的是因为喜欢才去做那样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的能力我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就把诺亚的能力拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是你要的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还装作没有注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切 要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们就这样回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才那个令人不快的梦是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还真敢让我看到那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这你就懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我所说的真相的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 开始还以为你只是单纯地让我看到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但后来发现并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看到的是你不愿意想起的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 你的能力是在梦中看到对方的心理阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在这里做什么呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被锁在仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}独自度过几个小时 直到巡夜的老师到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不算什么事 但我还是没办法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那三个人的要更加过分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来事件不是他们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是因为被冤枉才变成了现在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有在听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 你已经不用去在意那些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然已经尿湿了裤子 也是没办法的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然能忍受那么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然特意跑过来和我说这些 果然差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚已经决定以后就四个人一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请不要再来打扰我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是来说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想说的是 我是想帮你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也非常想帮那三人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此…一开始你就这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是 一开始就应该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为和那三个人接吻之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚一直在找帮助他们的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想怎么帮助那三个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他们恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢复原样？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚觉得他们能得到魔女的能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以恢复成以前的学校中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过幸亏计划被前辈们制止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三个人本来就很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要离开诺亚 很快就可以恢复到以前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚可是有魔女的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小冴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们几个…想做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本没有人相信我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明什么都没干 还被当成学校的问题儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敬吾 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莲也住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们只能永远四个人过校园生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才还一无所知的家伙 少在那里臭屁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我臭屁的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你们几个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因为你们几个这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成天畏畏缩缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诺亚才那么痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种事 你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 不知道该怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是啊 首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先做点让诺亚开心的事不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿到模拟店的经营权了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三个一年级好像也解除误会 回头是岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…不要缠着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.53,0:24:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我好像喜欢上前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说 说什么蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前辈 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…等等…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 把部室当什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是山田那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泷川同学的魔力 说不定还有其他效果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她不是能够接触到人内心最脆弱的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}前辈 我们一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.85,0:25:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接触一方与被接触的都能感受彼此的心情 互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.02,0:25:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样的效果吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那两个人 在某种程度上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定有相似之处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.38,0:26:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天约会呢 上午肯定去逛街
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.42,0:26:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后看完电影 在咖啡厅吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.55,0:26:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下集 山田君与七个魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.72,0:27:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.09,0:27:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先把今天的行程给我改了
